            <description><![CDATA[<div id="page-content" class="rich_media_area_primary">      <div class="rich_media_area_primary_inner">                                                        <div id="img-content" class="rich_media_wrp">                    <h1 class="rich_media_title " id="activity-name">            起来，饥寒交迫的奴隶——非洲的“星星之火"，开始燎原          </h1>          <div id="meta_content" class="rich_media_meta_list">                                      <span id="copyright_logo" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight rich_media_meta icon_appmsg_tag appmsg_title_tag weui-wa-hotarea">原创</span>                                                      <span class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text">                                                                                    <span role="link" tabindex="0" id="js_author_name" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight rich_media_meta_link weui-wa-hotarea" datarewardsn="" datatimestamp="" datacanreward="0">陆连烽</span>                                                                            </span>                                                                                                      <span class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_nickname" id="profileBt">              <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight weui-wa-hotarea" id="js_name">                老朱聊天下              </a>              <div id="js_profile_qrcode" aria-hidden="true" class="profile_container" style="display:none;">                <div class="profile_inner">                  <strong class="profile_nickname">老朱聊天下</strong>                  <img class="profile_avatar" id="js_profile_qrcode_img" src="" alt="">                  <p class="profile_meta">                  <label class="profile_meta_label">微信号</label>                  <span class="profile_meta_value">gh_b3c90afa8932</span>                  </p>                  <p class="profile_meta">                  <label class="profile_meta_label">功能介绍</label>                  <span class="profile_meta_value">比较能喷，擅长将复杂的世界地缘政治大饼馒头化。</span>                  </p>                </div>                <span class="profile_arrow_wrp" id="js_profile_arrow_wrp">                  <i class="profile_arrow arrow_out"></i>                  <i class="profile_arrow arrow_in"></i>                </span>              </div>            </span>            <em id="publish_time" class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text"></em>            <em id="js_ip_wording_wrp" class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text" role="option" style="display: none;">发表于<span id="js_ip_wording"></span></em>                      </div>                                                                                                                  <div id="js_tags" class="article-tag__list" data-len="2">                                        <div class="article-tag-card__title">收录于合集</div>              <div class="article-tags">                                                      <div class="article-tag__item-wrp js_tag weui-wa-hotarea js_wx_tap_highlight wx_tap_link" data-url="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/appmsgalbum?__biz=Mzg3MDIxOTM2OQ==&amp;action=getalbum&amp;album_id=1608866185972891650#wechat_redirect" data-tag_id="" data-album_id="1608866185972891650" data-tag_source="4" role="link" tabindex="0" aria-labelledby="js_article_tag_name__1608866185972891650 js_a11y_comma js_article_tag_num__1608866185972891650 js_article_tag_tips__1608866185972891650">                      <span aria-hidden="true" id="js_article_tag_name__1608866185972891650" class="article-tag__item">#大国博弈</span>                                              <span aria-hidden="true" class="article-tag__item-num">                          <span id="js_article_tag_num__1608866185972891650">464</span>                          <span id="js_article_tag_tips__1608866185972891650" class="weui-hidden_abs">个</span>                        </span>                                          </div>                                      <div class="article-tag__item-wrp js_tag weui-wa-hotarea js_wx_tap_highlight wx_tap_link" data-url="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/appmsgalbum?__biz=Mzg3MDIxOTM2OQ==&amp;action=getalbum&amp;album_id=2553783792751116290#wechat_redirect" data-tag_id="" data-album_id="2553783792751116290" data-tag_source="4" role="link" tabindex="0" aria-labelledby="js_article_tag_name__2553783792751116290 js_a11y_comma js_article_tag_num__2553783792751116290 js_article_tag_tips__2553783792751116290">                      <span aria-hidden="true" id="js_article_tag_name__2553783792751116290" class="article-tag__item">#亲历欧美衰败进行时</span>                                              <span aria-hidden="true" class="article-tag__item-num">                          <span id="js_article_tag_num__2553783792751116290">37</span>                          <span id="js_article_tag_tips__2553783792751116290" class="weui-hidden_abs">个</span>                        </span>                                          </div>                                                </div>                      </div>                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            <div class="rich_media_content js_underline_content                       autoTypeSetting24psection            " id="js_content" style="visibility: hidden;"><p><span style="font-size: 20px;">一个国家的现政权，零星的开上几枪，然后就被推翻了，这，就是神奇的非洲。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px;">非洲的军事政变，就像家长便饭一样此起彼伏。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px;">2022年9月30日，十几名士兵夺取了布基纳法索国家电视台的控制权，宣布解散9个月前同样通过军事政变上台的政府，同时发表声明，</span><span style="font-size: 20px;">称易卜拉欣·特拉奥雷将成为布基纳法索新的军政府领导人。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px;">彼时，雷哥还在几百公里外的边境线上与伊斯兰极端组织浴血奋战。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px;">3天后，一支全副武装的车队驶进首都，一辆装甲运兵车的炮塔里，露出了雷哥略显稚气的脸。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-ratio="0.4425403225806452" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/LVTUeINJMKZ83U91tABBhJA4Wah0syzscoicx0sc7KyqYc8AJVRX4sld9j3faDONWZJsoGibia9ptKBtDnLNJDKfQ/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="992" style=""></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px;">雷哥在努力憋着不让自己笑出来。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px;">想来，这么轻而易举地便夺取了政权，让他也觉得可笑吧。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px;">迎接雷哥的人群欢呼声鼎沸，民众激动地挥舞着俄罗斯国旗。<br></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px;">是的，你没看错，和上周发生军事政变夺取政权的尼日尔一样，布基纳法索政变发生后，街头民众挥舞的也是俄罗斯的国旗。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px;">19天后，雷哥宣誓就任过渡政府总统。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px;">没有任何证据证明是雷哥发动的政变，但雷哥成为了过渡政府的总统却是事实。<br></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px;">如此你明白，老朱在大前天的文章中所说的、上周在圣彼德堡举行的<span style='background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;'>第二届俄罗斯-非洲峰会后的合影中，</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.034em;">“</span><span style='background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;'>布基纳法索，按面积、按人口，按经济总量，无论从哪个角度，这个小国都在非洲排不上号，可是，雷哥却站在了普京的身旁“的原因了吧？</span></span></p><p><span style='background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-size: 20px;'>彼时，对于雷哥夺取政权一事，西方国家纷纷表示谴责，俄罗斯公开表达了对政变的支持，厨子更是专门发表了声明，表达了对雷哥的支持：”我向易卜拉欣*特拉奥雷上尉致敬并支持他。“<br></span></p><p><span style='background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-size: 20px;'>是的，上尉。</span></p><p><span style='background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-size: 20px;'>彼时的雷哥还只是个普通的低职军官。</span></p><p><span style='background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-size: 20px;'>不管政变是否是雷哥发起的，但一个小小的上尉能脱颖而出、成为过渡政府的总统，都足以说明，这，是个人物。</span></p><p><span style='font-size: 20px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;'>大家再瞅一眼雷哥：<br></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-ratio="0.4184239733629301" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/LVTUeINJMKZ83U91tABBhJA4Wah0syzsMck75l5MFxibe0NQib0qBrgDUJUlwqEFKRmUl7ncLpbmmYV2S4qianCsw/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="901" style=""></p><p><span style="font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;"></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px;">是不是稚气脱的很快？</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px;">战争催人成熟。</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style='font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 20px;'>有传闻说，雷哥毕业于石家庄陆军指挥学院，老朱感觉可能性不大，不仅是因为没有主流媒体报道过，更重要的是，如果真的在中国学过军事指挥，雷哥不可能在就职总统前还只是个小小的上尉。</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style='font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 20px;'>瞎推理的，大家看罢一笑而过好了。<br></span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style='font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 20px;'>雷哥一上台，先做了一件事，驱逐了法国在本国的驻军，这一招深知民心。</span><span style='background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 20px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;'>然后，雷哥下令禁止本国向法国和美国出口铀，并且，声明</span><span style='background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 20px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;'>，自己掌权不会太久，国家很快会选出新政府。</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style='font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 20px;'><span style='font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 20px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'>血与火中淬炼出来的军人</span><span style='font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 20px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'>，</span><span style='font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 20px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'>不贪财，不恋权，这种</span><span style='font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 20px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'>人最让西方头</span><span style='font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 20px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'>疼。</span></span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style='font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 20px;'><span style='font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 20px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'>一张图和一个数据，来证明一下，非洲的亲西方政府为何那么容易被推翻：</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-ratio="1" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/LVTUeINJMKZ83U91tABBhJA4Wah0syzsBoRxKMyH0WWo0plLnkzY7Jnp9SGuYAiazQsJGnrDnFjL5o64ZPEGZHw/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="540" style=""></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><br></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style='font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 20px;'>时至今日，法国依然每年从非洲攫取超过6000亿欧元的财富。</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style='font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 20px;'>非洲国家的人民不傻，知道谁才能保住自己国家的利益。<br></span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style='font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 20px;'>布基纳法索军事政变成功10个月后，尼日尔有样学样，通过军事政变推翻了亲西方的政府。<br></span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style='font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 20px;'>上张图：</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-ratio="0.7819650067294751" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/LVTUeINJMKZ83U91tABBhJA4Wah0syzsOx8aiaPwnw7NbJFtuPUP9M5eZnnBiaX78f8eF0txm8qXwfKydicgdmxhQ/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="743" style=""></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px;">看到了么，尼日尔大学生手中挥舞的，也是俄罗斯的国旗。</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style='font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 20px;'>虽然美国排除了尼日尔政变是俄操纵的，但还是有越来越多的迹象表明，非洲的”红色星星之火“确是老克格勃布的局，并且，不排除这一切的背后</span><span style='background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 20px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;'>有某个东方大国的影子。</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="font-size: 20px;">近一年多来，俄外长拉夫罗夫动不动就往非洲跑，中俄各种与非洲举行论坛，有谁敢说，这样的频繁往来，种下的不是“思想的星星之火”？<br></span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;font-size: 20px;">“非洲某国的房顶掉下来一片瓦，砸到了三个中国人，一个是中兴的，俩是华为的”，多年以前，这个梗便在网上流传。</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;font-size: 20px;">我国大力在非洲建基站、将自己淘汰的手机运到非洲，只是为了消化过剩过时的产能吗？那格局未免就有点小了。</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 82, 255);letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 20px;">“我们这一代人不明白这一点：拥有如此多财富（矿产和自然资源）的非洲怎么会成为当今世界上最贫穷的大陆？”，</span></p><p><span style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 20px;">这是雷哥的话。</span></p><p><span style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 20px;">这样的质疑，不止雷哥有，非洲每个国家的人民都有。</span></p><p><span style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 20px;">互联网时代，人们可以通过手机了解外面的世界，每个非洲人都看到了其它国家的真实生活，瞅瞅别人，再看看自己，他们能不去想问题到底出在哪儿?     </span></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px;">来自国际货币基金组织的数据：2022年马里人均GDP为858美元，在全球有数据的国家中倒数第17名；布基纳法索人均GDP为825美元，倒数第14名。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px;">这样的数据，非洲人民也能查到。<br></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px;">是谁一直在掠夺非洲？<br></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px;">一张图给出了答案：</span></p><p><br></p><p><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-ratio="1.0921875" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/LVTUeINJMKZ83U91tABBhJA4Wah0syzsbtSnuwm1VOvdNCCP8crABM8gJM7MrJQInCOq4dgfrTF4GNqHC6yialA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640"></p><p><br></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style='font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(0, 82, 255);font-size: 20px;'>“每次帝国主义拉动手中的操控线时，我们非洲国家领导人应该停止像木偶一样活动。”</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style='font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(0, 82, 255);font-size: 20px;'>"不反抗的奴隶不值得怜悯，非洲联盟必须停止谴责那些决定与西方傀儡政权作斗争的非洲人！”<br></span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style='font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 20px;'>这还是雷哥的原话。</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style='font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 20px;'>雷哥用自己的观察，告诉非洲人民，我们的苦难是因为西方的掠夺，我们的政府是西方殖民主义利益的代言人。</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style='font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(0, 82, 255);font-size: 20px;'>“我们不要钱，我们只要非洲人不再忍饥挨饿，可以过上幸福有尊严的生活”。</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style='font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 20px;'>这依旧是雷哥的原话。</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style='font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 20px;'>这样的心声，不止雷哥有，不止政变成功了的布基纳法索、马里、尼日尔3国的人民有，整个非洲的人民都有。</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style='font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.578px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);font-size: 20px;'>“非洲受西方政权奴役的时代已经结束，争取完全独立的战斗已经打响......要么是祖国，要么是死亡“；</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style='font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(0, 82, 255);font-size: 20px;'>“本世纪，非洲将用自己的资源发展自己！”<br></span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="font-size: 20px;">这铿锵有力的声音，太有震撼力了。</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="font-size: 20px;">至此，老朱大前天在文章中所说的，雷哥<span style='background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;'>极有可能成为非洲反殖民统治的领军人物，你是不是也开始有点相信了？</span></span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="font-size: 20px;">站在客观的角度讲，就算布基纳法索、马里、尼日尔三国加起来，也不是一个法国的对手，更不要说美国和欧盟都不会袖手旁观了，可是，反抗殖民统治的人背后有人民，有中俄。</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="font-size: 20px;">非洲的人民在觉醒，三把星星之火，必将在整个非洲燎原。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;list-style: none;text-align: center;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 20px;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">起来 饥寒交迫的奴隶</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;list-style: none;text-align: center;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 20px;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">起来 全世界受苦的人</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;list-style: none;text-align: center;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 20px;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">满腔的热血已经沸腾 要为真理而斗争</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;list-style: none;text-align: center;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 20px;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">旧世界打个落花流水 奴隶们起来 起来</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;list-style: none;text-align: center;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 20px;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">不要说我们一无所有 我们要做天下的主人</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;list-style: none;text-align: center;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 20px;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">这是最后的斗争 团结起来到明天</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;list-style: none;text-align: center;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 20px;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">英特纳雄耐尔就一定要实现</span></strong></span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><br></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="font-size: 20px;">此时此刻，《国际歌》正在非洲唱响。</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;"><span style="font-size: 20px;">啤酒饮料矿泉水，花生瓜子火腿肠……<br></span></p><p style="display: none;"><mp-style-type data-value="3"></mp-style-type></p></div>          <script type="text/javascript" nonce="1112913860" reportloaderror>            var first_sceen__time = (+new Date());            if ("" == 1 && document.getElementById('js_content')) {              document.getElementById('js_content').addEventListener("selectstart",function(e){ e.preventDefault(); });            }          </script>        </div>                        <div id="js_tags_preview_toast" class="article-tag__error-tips" style="display: none;">预览时标签不可点</div>                        <div id="content_bottom_area" class="rich_media_tool_area"></div>              </div>    </div>]]></description>
